longBusinessSummary: Indoor Harvest Corp. focuses on leveraging technology and planning on vertical farming, building integrated agriculture, controlled environment agriculture, and aeroponic cultivation in the United States. It develops proprietary high pressure aeroponic cultivation system designs, as well as flood and drain, and floating raft designs for cannabis and other agriculture products. The company offers Modular HP-Aeroponics, Low Tide VFRack, and Shallow Raft VFRack platforms under the Indoor Harvest brand. Indoor Harvest Corp. was founded in 2011 and is based in Austin, Texas.
